---
/*
  Founder — credibility-first trust layer (promoted from the footer).
  One idea: a real, accountable person handles your site — not an
  agency queue. Trust without testimonials: personal accountability,
  no lock-in, nationwide, jargon-free.
*/
---
<section id="founder" class="section section-tinted" aria-labelledby="founder-heading">
  <div class="container founder-band">

    <div class="founder-media reveal">
      <span class="founder-ring" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <img
        class="founder-photo"
        src="/assets/images/founder-image.jpeg"
        alt="Mandip Sapkota, founder of ReadyStack Digital"
        width="240" height="240" loading="lazy" decoding="async"
      />
      <div class="founder-badge">
        Handles every account personally
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="founder-content reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="eyebrow">Who you'll actually work with</div>
      <h2 id="founder-heading" class="section-h2">
        You deal with the person who<br>
        <span class="text-amber">builds and manages your site.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="founder-quote">
        “I started ReadyStack to give small businesses the fast, secure, well-managed website
        that bigger companies pay agencies for — without the agency runaround. I handle every
        build and every monthly check myself, so you always talk to the person who knows your
        site best.”
      </p>
      <p class="founder-sign">— Mandip Sapkota, Founder</p>

      <ul class="founder-points" role="list">
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 8.5 6.5 12 13 4.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>One specialist, start to finish — no handoffs</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 8.5 6.5 12 13 4.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>No lock-in contracts — stay because it works</li>
        <li><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 8.5 6.5 12 13 4.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Nationwide support, plain-English updates</li>
      </ul>

      <a href="/contact#book" class="btn btn-amber btn-lg magnetic">
        <span>Book a free 30-min call</span>
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M3 9h12M9 3l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #founder { padding-block: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem); }
  .founder-band {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(220px, 320px) 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Media */
  .founder-media { position: relative; justify-self: center; width: min(280px, 70vw); }
  .founder-photo {
    position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 1; border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover; object-position: center top;
    border: 2px solid rgba(245,158,11,.5);
    box-shadow: 0 28px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.5), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  }
  .founder-ring {
    position: absolute; inset: -8px; z-index: 0; border-radius: 50%;
    background: conic-gradient(from 0deg, #F59E0B, #FCD34D, rgba(245,158,11,.1), #F59E0B);
    filter: blur(3px); opacity: .55; animation: f-spin 10s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes f-spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
  .founder-badge {
    position: absolute; z-index: 2; left: 50%; bottom: -14px; translate: -50% 0;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .45rem; white-space: nowrap;
    padding: .42rem .8rem; border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(11,13,16,.9); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.35);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .66rem; letter-spacing: .04em; color: rgba(255,255,255,.78);
  }

  /* Content */
  .founder-content { max-width: 640px; }
  .founder-quote {
    margin: 1.25rem 0 .5rem; max-width: 56ch;
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.3vw, 1.22rem); line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.82);
  }
  .founder-sign { margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--amber-300); font-weight: var(--weight-semibold); }
  .founder-points { list-style: none; margin: 0 0 1.75rem; padding: 0; display: grid; gap: .6rem; }
  .founder-points li {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .6rem;
    font-size: .96rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.78);
  }
  .founder-points svg { flex: 0 0 auto; }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .founder-band { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; gap: 3rem; }
    .founder-content { max-width: 600px; margin-inline: auto; }
    #founder .eyebrow { justify-content: center; }
    .founder-quote { margin-inline: auto; }
    .founder-points { justify-items: center; }
    .founder-points li { justify-content: center; text-align: left; }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .founder-ring { animation: none !important; } }
</style>
